' SD-05. UC-005 삼면 장애물 감지 후 후진
' Related Use Case: UC-005. 삼면 장애물 감지 후 후진
' Intent: 전방, 좌측, 우측이 모두 막힌 상태에서 정지 후 후진하고 다시 회피 방향 선택으로 넘기는 흐름을 표현한다.
' Note: 후진할 수 없고 좌우가 모두 막힌 경우 정지 상태를 유지한다.

@startuml SD_05_UC005_Backward_On_Three_Side_Obstacle
title SD-05 - UC-005 삼면 장애물 감지 후 후진

actor "센서 입력" as Sensor
participant "RVC SW Controller" as Controller
participant "SensorState" as SensorState
participant "AutomaticCleaning" as Cleaning
participant "AvoidanceDecision" as AvoidanceDecision
participant "MovementCommand" as MovementCommand
actor "주행 장치" as Drive

Sensor -> Controller: reportObstacleState(frontObstacleDetected=true, leftObstacleDetected=true, rightObstacleDetected=true)
activate Controller
Controller -> SensorState: updateObstacles(frontObstacleDetected=true, leftObstacleDetected=true, rightObstacleDetected=true)
Controller -> Cleaning: handleThreeSideObstacle(SensorState)
activate Cleaning
Cleaning -> SensorState: isThreeSideBlocked()
SensorState --> Cleaning: true
Cleaning -> Cleaning: changeStatus(BLOCKED)
Cleaning -> MovementCommand: create(STOP)
MovementCommand --> Cleaning: stopCommand
Cleaning -> Drive: stop()
Cleaning -> AvoidanceDecision: evaluateBackwardRequired(SensorState)
AvoidanceDecision --> Cleaning: backwardRequired=true

alt 후진 가능
    Cleaning -> MovementCommand: create(MOVE_BACKWARD)
    MovementCommand --> Cleaning: backwardCommand
    Cleaning -> Drive: moveBackward()
    Drive --> Cleaning: backwardCompleted()
    Sensor -> Controller: reportSideObstacleState(leftObstacleDetected=false, rightObstacleDetected=false)
    Controller -> SensorState: updateSideObstacles(leftObstacleDetected=false, rightObstacleDetected=false)
    Controller -> Cleaning: selectAvoidanceDirection(SensorState)
    note right of Cleaning: UC-003으로 전환해 회피 방향 선택
else 후진 불가 및 좌우 모두 막힘
    Cleaning -> AvoidanceDecision: markNoAvailableDirection()
    AvoidanceDecision --> Cleaning: availableDirection=false
    Cleaning -> MovementCommand: create(STOP)
    MovementCommand --> Cleaning: stopCommand
    Cleaning -> Drive: stop()
    Cleaning -> Cleaning: keepStatus(STOPPED)
end

Cleaning --> Controller: threeSideObstacleHandled()
deactivate Cleaning
deactivate Controller
@enduml
